Package: easyMake
Type: Package
Title: What the Package Does (Title Case)
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Gordon", "Shotwell", email = "g.e.shotwell@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: easyMake provides a simple way to generate Makefiles. It detects
    dependencies between R scripts, plots a graph of those dependencies, and
    generates a buildable Makefile based on them.
License: GPL-2
LazyData: TRUE
URL: https://github.com/GShotwell/easyMake
BugReports: https://github.com/GShotwell/easyMake/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0),
Imports:
    igraph,
    dplyr,
    ggraph,
    tools,
    stringr
Remotes: thomasp85/ggraph
Suggests:
    knitr,
    testthat
VignetteBuilder: knitr
